<div class="row-fluid explain">
  <div class="explain-row">
    <div class="explain-title">
      <h2>Anong mga Maaaring Mapanalunan?</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div>
        <%= image_tag "shuffle.jpg", id: "shuffle" %> 
      </div>
      <div>
        Brand New iPod Shuffle bilang first prize kapag nakakuha ng 125 points o pataas
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row">
      <div class="span2 offset3" style="color: #f1c40f">
        <i class="icon-question-sign"></i>
        <div class="desc">
          1st Prize
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:15px">
          Ang mapapanalunan ng may pinakamaraming napadalo sa susunod na pulong 
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="span2" style="color: #bdc3c7">
        <i class="icon-question-sign"></i>
        <div class="desc">
          2nd Prize
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:15px">
          Ang mapapanalunan ng sumunod 
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="span2" style="color: #c0392b">
        <i class="icon-question-sign"></i>
        <div class="desc">
          3rd Prize
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="explain-row">
      <div>
        Ang 1st, 2nd at 3rd prizes ay ire-reveal namin sa susunod na pulong 
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row">
      <div class="span1 offset3" style="font-size: 40px">
        <i class="icon-user"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="span5 consolation">
        Mananalo ng consolation prize ang lahat ng mga napadalo ng nanalo ng 1st prize 
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explain-title explain-row">
      <h2>Paano Manalo?</h2>
    </div>

    <div style="color: #7f8c8d">
    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row">
      <div class="span2 offset2" style="font-size: 40px;">
        <span class="circle" style="background: #9b59b6"><i class="icon-thumbs-up"></i></span>
      </div>
      <div class="span5 consolation">
        Ang labanan dito ay paramihan ng mapapadalong Kadiwa sa susunod na pulong sa darating na Disyembre 
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row-less-margin">
      <div class="span2 offset2" style="font-size: 40px">
        <span class="circle" style="background: #2ecc71"><i class="icon-star-empty"></i></span>
      </div>
      <div class="span5 consolation">
        Ang mananalo ng 1st prize at makakakuha ng 125 points pataas ang mananalo ng ating grand prize na brand new iPod Shuffle
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row-less-margin">
      <div class="span2 offset2" style="font-size: 40px">
        <span class="circle" style="background: #3498db"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></span>
      </div>
      <div class="span5 consolation">
        Sumali sa pamamagitan ng pagsign-up through Facebook 
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row-less-margin">
      <div class="span2 offset2" style="font-size: 40px">
        <span class="circle" style="background: #e74c3c"><i class="icon-plus"></i></span>
      </div>
      <div class="span5 consolation">
        Mang-imbita ng marami online sa pamamagitan ng pagbibigay ng invite link na maaari niyong ma-copy-paste sa inyong dashboard page. Tandaan na kailangan na sa invite link niyo sila magsignup upang sila ay maging 'invite' niyo
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row-less-margin">
      <div class="span2 offset2" style="font-size: 40px">
        <span class="circle" style="background: #e67e22"><i class="icon-calendar"></i></span>
      </div>
      <div class="span5 consolation">
        Laging i-remind ang inyong naging 'invite' na sumama sa inyo sa susunod na pulong
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid prizes explain-row-less-margin">
      <div class="span2 offset2" style="font-size: 40px">
        <span class="circle" style="background: #1abc9c"><i class="icon-bell"></i></span>
      </div>
      <div class="span5 consolation">
        Dalhin sa pulong ang inyong 'invite' ang magregister sa attendance. Ang bawat isa sa inyong napadalo ng pulong ay may katumbas na 5 points
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid explain-row">
      <div>&copy; The Ultimate Kadiwa Invite Challenge 2013</div>
      <div>Email the author of this website at nmfdelacruz@gmail.com</div>
    </div>


  </div>
</div>
